Name: Field Rations
Types: Rations
Components: Salted Flour, Water, Iron Thistle
Description: This hard tack, while not especially satisfying, keeps the body going. When consumed, this ration allows the adventurer to get the most out of any respite. If a creature spends a Hit Dice during the rest, they may add DAMAGE1-2DAMAGEd8 to the total number of hit points recovered.
